<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, July 8 (Xinhua) -- A total of 3,477 cases of cholera
have been reported in Zimbabwe with 255 deaths since the outbreak
of the disease in January this year, the Zimbabwean Health and
Child Welfare Ministry said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
