that his ministry has continued to step up its awareness campaigns
and set up cholera camps in all provinces to curb the spread of
the disease.
</P>
<P>
The World Health Organization (WHO) said recently it supported
the ministry's efforts to curb cholera through preventive measures
rather than using vaccines, the Zimbabwe News Agency Ziana
reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
