<HEADLINE> Molotov Cocktails Thrown into U.S. Embassy in Ukraine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Two Molotov cocktails were thrown into
the U.S. Embassy in Kiev, Ukraine, in the early morning of
Wednesday, but the attack caused no injuries or property damage,
embassy officials said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
An eyewitness said three unidentified masked men threw "
something like Molotov cocktails" through the windows of the U.S.
Embassy.
</P>
<P>
Embassy officials said that they received no threatening calls
prior to the attack and that nobody has claimed responsibility for
it. The attack was considered only as an act by hooligans, they
said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
