<HEADLINE> Two Government Soldiers Killed in Southern Philippines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 9 (Xinhua) -- Suspected two young recruits of the
terrorist Abu Sayyaf Group Thursday killed two army troopers
