On bilateral economic and trade cooperation, Zhu said that
China and Japan are important economic and trade partners and have
established a kind of cooperative framework with complementarity
at certain advantageous points, diversity in cooperation, and
stability.
</P>
<P>
This has brought great benefits to both countries and played an
