<HEADLINE> Zhu and Obuchi Hold Talks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 9 (Xinhua)-- The ongoing visit to China by
Japanese Prime Minister Keizo Obuchi is of great importance,
Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji said here today.
</P>
