and his Japanese counterpart had had a frank and in-depth exchange
of views on some important issues during a closed-door session.
</P>
<P>
This has helped increase mutual understanding and expand
common grounds, and served to push the bilateral political
relations onto a right and healthy track, Zhu added.
</P>
<P>
