overall plan for bilateral cooperation in various fields in the
form of a joint press communique.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that he is glad to see the results are being
implemented through joint efforts and have scored periodical
achievements.
</P>
<P>
It is in the fundamental interests of the two peoples to
continue to consolidate the political foundation of the Sino-
Japanese relations, and to further promote and carry out solid
cooperation in various sectors, Zhu said.
</P>
