wins in five outings, and Poland took the second place after a 3-1
victory over Turkey.
</P>
<P>
Russia was the only other squad that remained unbeaten after
defeating Estonia 3-0 for a fifth straight win to top Group D,
while Japan also qualified for the quarter-finals after its 3-1
victory over the Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
In the quarter-finals, Germany will face Poland, Spain takes on
South Korea, the United States plays Japan while Russia meets
Belgium. 
