<HEADLINE> Taliban Say Osama Is in Afghanistan: Report </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, July 8 (Xinhua) -- Afghanistan's ruling Taliban
Thursday admitted Osama bin Laden, the suspected terrorist wanted
